edu.cnm.deepdive.celestialbodies.model.entity

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.celestialbodies.model.entity.User

  • public class User
extends Object
    Encapsulates the desired information to be collected regarding a user of the star app. Room and GSon annotations are used to specify entity & attribute mapping for database persistence, and property mapping for JSON serialization/deserialization mapping.
